<div class="nbunit" id="edn129">  129  These details do not appear in the fragment of letter that Shaun cites. He is overstepping his text or is in possession of information withheld from us. The relation between ALP's letter as it appears here and the exoneration/exculpation of HCE is obscure, but it becomes clearer in Book IV where the full text of the famous letter is given and the role of the sneak, Magrath, is clarified.  </div>
